<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>후쿠오카 2박3일 — 30개월 아기와 함께하는 여행</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script src="https://code.iconify.design/iconify-icon/1.0.7/iconify-icon.min.js"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap">
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          fontFamily: { sans: ['Geist', 'sans-serif'] },
          colors: {
            neutral: {
              50: '#fafafa', 100: '#f5f5f5', 200: '#e5e5e5',
              300: '#d4d4d4', 400: '#a3a3a3', 500: '#737373',
              600: '#525252', 700: '#404040', 800: '#262626', 900: '#171717'
            }
          },
          animation: {
            'fade-up': 'fadeUp 0.8s ease-out forwards',
            'clip-in': 'clipIn 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.25,1,0.5,1) both',
          },
          keyframes: {
            fadeUp: {
              '0%': { opacity: 0, transform: 'translateY(20px)' },
              '100%': { opacity: 1, transform: 'translateY(0)' }
            },
            clipIn: {
              '0%': { opacity: 0, clipPath: 'inset(0 0 100% 0)' },
              '100%': { opacity: 1, clipPath: 'inset(0 0 0 0)' }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
  <style>
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif; }
    .day-section:target { scroll-margin-top: 80px; }
    .checklist-item input:checked + label { text-decoration: line-through; color: #a3a3a3; }
    .timeline-dot::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: -29px;
      top: 6px;
      width: 14px;
      height: 14px;
      background: #2563eb;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 3px solid #eff6ff;
      z-index: 10;
    }
    .timeline-dot::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: -23px;
      top: 20px;
      width: 2px;
      height: calc(100% + 12px);
      background: #e5e5e5;
    }
    .timeline-dot:last-child::after { display: none; }
    .toast {
      animation: toastIn 0.4s ease-out, toastOut 0.4s ease-in 2s forwards;
    }
    @keyframes toastIn {
      0% { transform: translateY(20px); opacity: 0; }
      100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
    }
    @keyframes toastOut {
      0% { opacity: 1; }
      100% { opacity: 0; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-neutral-50 text-neutral-900 antialiased">

  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 backdrop-blur-xl bg-white/70 border-b border-neutral-200/50">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="#" class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <iconify-icon icon="mdi:airplane-takeoff" class="text-xl text-blue-600"></iconify-icon>
        <span class="font-semibold tracking-tight">아기랑 후쿠오카</span>
      </a>
      <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 text-sm font-medium text-neutral-500">
        <a href="#preparation" class="hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors">준비물</a>
        <a href="#day1" class="hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors">1일차</a>
        <a href="#day2" class="hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors">2일차</a>
        <a href="#day3" class="hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors">3일차</a>
        <a href="#tips" class="hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors">아기팁</a>
        <a href="#restaurants" class="hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors">식당</a>
      </div>
      <button id="mobileMenuBtn" class="md:hidden p-2">
        <iconify-icon icon="mdi:menu" class="text-2xl"></iconify-icon>
      </button>
    </div>
    <!-- Mobile Menu -->
    <div id="mobileMenu" class="hidden md:hidden bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-xl border-b border-neutral-200/50 px-6 pb-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-sm font-medium text-neutral-600">
        <a href="#preparation" class="py-2 hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors">준비물</a>
        <a href="#day1" class="py-2 hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors">1일차</a>
        <a href="#day2" class="py-2 hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors">2일차</a>
        <a href="#day3" class="py-2 hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors">3일차</a>
        <a href="#tips" class="py-2 hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors">아기팁</a>
        <a href="#restaurants" class="py-2 hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors">식당</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-12 px-6 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
      <div class="absolute top-20 left-1/4 w-72 h-72 bg-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-40 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
        <!-- Left -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-6">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-blue-50 rounded-full text-blue-600 text-sm font-medium">
            <iconify-icon icon="mdi:baby-carriage" class="text-lg"></iconify-icon>
            30개월 아기 동반 여행 가이드
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-medium tracking-tight leading-[0.95]">
            후쿠오카<br>
            <span class="text-neutral-400">2박 3일</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
            30개월 아기와 함께하는 첫 해외여행, 걱정 반 기대 반으로 준비한 후쿠오카 여행기입니다. 아기 친화적 코스와 실전 팁을 모았어요.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a href="#day1" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-neutral-900 text-white rounded-xl text-sm font-medium hover:scale-[0.975] transition-transform duration-400">
              일정 보기
              <iconify-icon icon="mdi:arrow-down" class="text-base"></iconify-icon>
            </a>
            <a href="#preparation" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium hover:bg-neutral-50 transition-colors">
              준비물 체크
              <iconify-icon icon="mdi:clipboard-check-outline" class="text-base"></iconify-icon>
            </a>
          </div>
          <!-- Quick Info Cards -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 pt-4">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-neutral-200/50 shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-600">1:40</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-1">비행시간(분)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-neutral-200/50 shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-2xl font-semibold text-emerald-600">2박</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-1">숙박 일정</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-neutral-200/50 shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-2xl font-semibold text-purple-600">30m</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-1">아기 월령</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Right Image -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative">
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_24px_60px_-32px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35)]">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/fukuoka-canal/600/720.jpg" alt="후쿠오카 운하" class="w-full h-[400px] lg:h-[520px] object-cover">
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 shadow-lg border border-neutral-100 flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <iconify-icon icon="mdi:weather-sunny" class="text-xl text-orange-500"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold">연중 온화</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-neutral-400">평균 15~28°C</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Overview Strip -->
  <section class="py-6 px-6 border-y border-neutral-200/50 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-6 text-center">
      <div>
        <iconify-icon icon="mdi:airplane" class="text-2xl text-blue-600"></iconify-icon>
        <div class="text-sm font-medium mt-1">인천→후쿠오카</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-neutral-400">직항 1시간 40분</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <iconify-icon icon="mdi:train" class="text-2xl text-emerald-600"></iconify-icon>
        <div class="text-sm font-medium mt-1">공항→덴진</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-neutral-400">지하철 12분</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <iconify-icon icon="mdi:currency-jpy" class="text-2xl text-orange-500"></iconify-icon>
        <div class="text-sm font-medium mt-1">환율</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-neutral-400">100엔 ≈ 920원</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <iconify-icon icon="mdi:wifi" class="text-2xl text-purple-600"></iconify-icon>
        <div class="text-sm font-medium mt-1">포켓와이파이</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-neutral-400">1일 3,000원대</div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-2 md:col-span-1">
        <iconify-icon icon="mdi:card-account-details" class="text-2xl text-pink-600"></iconify-icon>
        <div class="text-sm font-medium mt-1">교통카드</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-neutral-400">하야카카 필수!</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Preparation Section -->
  <section id="preparation" class="py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 bg-orange-50 rounded-full text-orange-600 text-xs font-medium mb-4">
          <iconify-icon icon="mdi:package-variant-closed"></iconify-icon>
          PREPARATION
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight">아기 여행 준비물 체크리스트</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 mt-3">체크박스를 클릭하면 준비 완료 표시가 됩니다</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- 카테고리 1: 필수 서류 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-neutral-200/50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-500">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <iconify-icon icon="mdi:passport" class="text-xl text-blue-600"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">필수 서류</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="doc1" class="w-4 h-4 accent-blue-600 rounded">
              <label for="doc1" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">여권 (아기 본인 여권 필수)</label>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="doc2" class="w-4 h-4 accent-blue-600 rounded">
              <label for="doc2" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">항공권 e-티켓 출력</label>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="doc3" class="w-4 h-4 accent-blue-600 rounded">
              <label for="doc3" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">숙소 예약 확인서</label>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="doc4" class="w-4 h-4 accent-blue-600 rounded">
              <label for="doc4" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">여행자보험 증서</label>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="doc5" class="w-4 h-4 accent-blue-600 rounded">
              <label for="doc5" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">가족관계증명서 (영문)</label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 카테고리 2: 아기 용품 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-neutral-200/50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-500">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-pink-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <iconify-icon icon="mdi:baby-face-outline" class="text-xl text-pink-600"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">아기 용품</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="baby1" class="w-4 h-4 accent-pink-600 rounded">
              <label for="baby1" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">기저귀 (여유 있게 1.5배)</label>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="baby2" class="w-4 h-4 accent-pink-600 rounded">
              <label for="baby2" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">물티슈 대용 휴지</label>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="baby3" class="w-4 h-4 accent-pink-600 rounded">
              <label for="baby3" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">젖병 / 물병 / 컵</label>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="baby4" class="w-4 h-4 accent-pink-600 rounded">
              <label for="baby4" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">아기 간식 (한국 것 필수)</label>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="baby5" class="w-4 h-4 accent-pink-600 rounded">
              <label for="baby5" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">아기 처방약 / 해열제</label>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="baby6" class="w-4 h-4 accent-pink-600 rounded">
              <label for="baby6" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">유모차 (가벼운 접이식)</label>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="baby7" class="w-4 h-4 accent-pink-600 rounded">
              <label for="baby7" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">아기띠 (케리어)</label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 카테고리 3: 의류 & 잡화 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-neutral-200/50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-500">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <iconify-icon icon="mdi:tshirt-crew-outline" class="text-xl text-emerald-600"></iconify-icon>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">의류 & 잡화</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="cloth1" class="w-4 h-4 accent-emerald-600 rounded">
              <label for="cloth1" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">겉옷 (일교차 대비 얇은 재킷)</label>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="cloth2" class="w-4 h-4 accent-emerald-600 rounded">
              <label for="cloth2" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">아기 여벌 옷 (하루 2벌씩)</label>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="cloth3" class="w-4 h-4 accent-emerald-600 rounded">
              <label for="cloth3" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">편한 신발 / 양말</label>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="cloth4" class="w-4 h-4 accent-emerald-600 rounded">
              <label for="cloth4" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">햇볕 가리개 모자</label>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="cloth5" class="w-4 h-4 accent-emerald-600 rounded">
              <label for="cloth5" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">젖병 세정제 / 브러시</label>
            </div>
            <div class="checklist-item flex items-center gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" id="cloth6" class="w-4 h-4 accent-emerald-600 rounded">
              <label for="cloth6" class="text-sm text-neutral-600 cursor-pointer">비닐봉지 (더러운 옷용)</label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Day 1 -->
  <section id="day1" class="day-section py-20 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-12">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xl font-semibold shadow-[0_8px_24px_-8px_rgba(37,99,235,0.5)]">1</div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight">DAY 1</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-400">인천 → 후쿠오카 공항 → 덴진 숙소 → 오호리 공원 → 캐널시티</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
        <!-- Timeline -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 relative pl-8 border-l-0">
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <!-- 항공 -->
            <div class="timeline-dot relative">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">오전</span>
                <span class="text-sm text-neutral-400">08:00 출발</span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">인천공항 → 후쿠오카공항</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
                아침 항공으로 출발! 공항에서 체크인 시 아기 유모차는 수하물로 부치고, 아기띠로 이동하세요. 탑승 시 아기용 귀마개(이어플러그) 꼭 챙기세요. 비행시간은 짧아 1시간 40분이면 도착합니다.
              </p>
              <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-100 rounded text-xs text-neutral-500">✈️ 직항 1:40</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-100 rounded text-xs text-neutral-500">👶 귀마개 필수</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-100 rounded text-xs text-neutral-500">🍼 이착륙 시 수분섭취</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 공항 → 숙소 -->
            <div class="timeline-dot relative">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-emerald-600 bg-emerald-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">오전</span>
                <span class="text-sm text-neutral-400">11:00</span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">공항 → 덴진 숙소 이동</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
                후쿠오카공항은 시내에서 매우 가깝습니다! 지하철 공항선으로 덴진까지 약 12분. 유모차 엘리베이터 위치는 역마다 있지만 미리 확인하면 좋습니다. 하야카카(교통카드)를 공항에서 먼저 구매하세요.
              </p>
              <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-100 rounded text-xs text-neutral-500">🚇 지하철 12분</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-100 rounded text-xs text-neutral-500">💳 하야카카 구매</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-100 rounded text-xs text-neutral-500">🏢 엘리베이터 확인</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 오호리 공원 -->
            <div class="timeline-dot relative">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-orange-600 bg-orange-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">오후</span>
                <span class="text-sm text-neutral-400">13:00</span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">오호리 공원 🌳 아기 산책 최고!</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
                후쿠오카 시민의 후원인 오호리 공원은 아기 유모차 산책에 최적화되어 있습니다. 넓은 호수 둘레길이 평탄하고, 일본식 정원도 있어 산책하기 좋습니다. 아기가 뛰어놀 잔디밭도 넓어요. 점심은 공원 근처 카페에서 가볍게!
              </p>
              <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-100 rounded text-xs text-neutral-500">🦆 오리 먹이주기</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-100 rounded text-xs text-neutral-500">🧺 피크닉 가능</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-100 rounded text-xs text-neutral-500">♿ 유모차 접근성 최상</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 캐널시티 -->
            <div class="timeline-dot relative">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-purple-600 bg-purple-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">저녁</span>
                <span class="text-sm text-neutral-400">17:00</span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">캐널시티 하카타 🛍️</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
                복합 쇼핑몰로 아기와 다니기 좋습니다. 실내라 날씨 상관없고, 라모네 광장의 분수쇼가 아기 눈길을 사로잡아요. 4F에 키즈플로어가 있어 놀이공간 활용 가능! 저녁은 라멘 스타디움에서 맛있게~
              </p>
              <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-100 rounded text-xs text-neutral-500">🎪 분수쇼</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-100 rounded text-xs text-neutral-500">👶 키즈플로어 4F</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-neutral-100 rounded text-xs text-neutral-500">🍜 라멘 스타디움</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Side Image -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-6">
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/ohori-park/600/400.jpg" alt="오호리 공원" class="w-full h-56 object-cover">
            <div class="p-4 bg-neutral-50">
              <p class="text-sm font-medium">오호리 공원</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400">아기 유모차 산책의 정석</p>
            </div>
