          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/canal-city-fukuoka/600/400.jpg" alt="캐널시티 하카타" class="w-full h-56 object-cover">
            <div class="p-4 bg-neutral-50">
              <p class="text-sm font-medium">캐널시티 하카타</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400">쇼핑+식사+아기놀이 한곳에</p>
